text = "This town built on a tree was inspired by a similar town populated by anthro birds from the Pocket God comic.
They weren't a big inspiration in the creation of Toures 
(I was inspired to make them because someone thought of the \"scavengers\" from Wings of Fire as birds,
and they're heavily inspired by the Patapon series' characters)
If you want to read the comic, it's been archived on Webtoon by at least one of the people who worked on it.
Some days, I really wish I could still play the Facebook version."
